		"body": "Reference links are converted to normal links when saved in the rich text editor. Add a note about this in the rich text editor notes.\r\n\r\nExample before Rich Text Editor:\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\n# Title\r\n\r\nA paragraph with a link to [Joplin on GitHub][joplin-github].\r\n\r\n[joplin-github]: https://github.com/laurent22/joplin\r\n```\r\n\r\nMarkdown after Rich Text Editor reformatting:\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\n# Title\r\n\r\nA paragraph with a link to [Joplin on GitHub](https://github.com/laurent22/joplin).\r\n```",
